---
import Layout from '~/layouts/InquiryLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<Layout metadata={{ title: 'Nozzle Clogging: Causes & Fixes — EVAPFit', ignoreTitleTemplate: true }}>
  <section class="overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 text-center sm:px-6 sm:py-20">
      <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-400/30 bg-slate-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-slate-200 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <Icon name="tabler:tools" class="h-4 w-4" /> Troubleshooting Guide
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Nozzle Clogging: Causes and How to Fix It</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-300">Identify and resolve spray nozzle clogging in your evaporative cooler's water distribution system.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-16">
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <h2>Common Causes</h2>
        <ul><li>Mineral scale buildup from hard water</li><li>Debris or dirt in water supply</li><li>Algae growth in water tank</li><li>Deteriorated nozzle material</li></ul>
        <h2>How to Fix</h2>
        <h3>1. Clean the Nozzle</h3><p>Remove the nozzle from the distribution pipe. Soak in white vinegar or descaling solution for 30 minutes. Use a fine needle to clear any remaining blockages.</p>
        <h3>2. Clean the Water System</h3><p>Drain and clean the water tank. Check and clean the water strainer/filter. Inspect the pump inlet for debris.</p>
        <h3>3. Replace if Needed</h3><p>If cleaning doesn't restore spray pattern or if the nozzle shows signs of deterioration, replace with a new spray nozzle.</p>
        <h3>4. Prevention</h3><p>Install a water strainer before the distribution system. Use water treatment tablets. Schedule quarterly cleaning and inspection.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 rounded-xl bg-teal-50 p-6 text-center dark:bg-teal-900/20">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-teal-800 dark:text-teal-200">Need replacement nozzles?</h3>
          <a href="/water-system/water-distribution-level/nozzle-spray-jet" class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-teal-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-700"><Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-4 w-4" /> Browse Spray Nozzles</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
